data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat in the heart of Saint Cloud, Florida! Nestled on a serene quarter-acre lot, this exquisite ranch-style luxury home offers the perfect blend of elegance and comfort. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a spacious 2-car garage, this residence promises a lifestyle of tranquility and sophistication.    Step inside and be captivated by the seamless fusion of modern design and timeless charm. The open-concept living area invites you to unwind by the cozy fireplace, where you can bask in the warmth of the flames on cooler evenings. Sunlight dances through large windows, illuminating the space and creating an inviting atmosphere that is perfect for both intimate gatherings and grand celebrations.    The heart of this home is undoubtedly the chef's kitchen, adorned with top-of-the-line appliances, granite countertops, and a stylish breakfast bar. Whether you're preparing a gourmet feast or a quick snack, the kitchen's layout ensures that every culinary endeavor is a joy.    Retreat to the luxurious primary suite, complete with an en-suite bathroom that exudes spa-like opulence. Dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower create an oasis of relaxation, offering a private escape from the bustle of daily life. The additional well-appointed bedrooms are perfect for family, guests, or even a dedicated home office space to meet your lifestyle needs.    Outside, your own slice of paradise awaits. The sprawling backyard beckons you to soak in the Florida sunshine while sipping your morning coffee or hosting memorable barbecues. The quarter-acre lot provides ample space for gardening, play, or creating your personal outdoor sanctuary.    Located minutes from the Florida Turnpike in the sought-after city of Saint Cloud, you'll have easy access to a plethora of amenities, including shops at Lake Nona, dining, parks, and entertainment options. Whether you're exploring the local charms or commuting to nearby Orlando, this prime location ensures that convenience is always at your fingertips.    Seize the opportunity to make this ranch-style luxury home your own and experience a lifestyle that's defined by elegance, comfort, and the beauty of Florida living. Don't miss your chance – schedule a viewing today and let your homeownership dreams come true in Saint Cloud!
